original_title: Big Time Rush: The City Is Ours - Live at Madison Square Garden
overview: Join Big Time Rush for a global livestream event. On November 23rd, relive the magic of the FOREVER TOUR at their sold-out show at Madison Square Garden! PLUS you’ll get exclusive behind the scenes footage from the show. This is a night you won’t want to miss.
title: Big Time Rush: The City Is Ours - Live at Madison Square Garden
